*Anđeo* je letio nad oblacima. (The angel flew above the clouds.)

*Anđela* je bila u belom odelu. (The angel was wearing white clothes.)

*Anđelima* su se činile sve smešne stvari. (Everything seemed funny to the angels.)

Istorija je puna *Anđela*. (History is full of angels.)

*Anđelu* su poslali da pomogne čoveku. (They sent an angel to help the man.)

*Anđele* su opisivali kao božanske biće. (They described angels as divine beings.)